metadata.name: neverland #01
metadata.description:
e9Art - return to neverland


it wasn’t until i was nearly 50 that i figured out what i wanted out of life: 

childlike wonder, joyful surprise, playful adventure … 

and then it took me a few more years to figure out what path would take me there.

as it turns out, that path was/is Art.

and

everything that has ever happened to me, both the good and the bad, has brought me to this moment.

all my life has been a training ground to prepare me for this now … 

for this adventure that i suddenly find myself plunged into … 

for this world of imagination and play and NFTs and AI text-to-image generators … 

for this return to Neverland …

digital art by e9Art using disco diffusion and photoshop, May 2022
